<br>
For example if I'm playing DAOC or Q3 or something, if I press FFGGH - where FF stands for activation, GG stands for next track and H confirms, Winamp will skip to the next track on my play list.<br>
<br>
I customed those commands myself, you can set them waht you want<br>
